Author: Sam H
Author-email: ll13s5h@leeds.ac.uk
License: UNKNOWN
Description: pyg3D
        ===============
        
        pyg3D is a simple library built on top of pyglet, to provide a simple 3D graphics
        library for python.
        
        Dependencies
        ----------------------------
        
        pyg3D requires:
        
        - pyglet
        - numpy
        - PyOpenGL
        
        Installation
        ----------------------------
        
        pyg3D can be installed through pip with the command
        ``pip install pyg3D``
